        "verses_html": "<div class=\"std-text\"> <p><span class=\"text 3John-1-1\" id=\"en-NIV-30660\"><sup class=\"versenum\">1\u00a0</sup>The elder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30660A\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30660A\" title=\"See cross-reference A\"&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30660A\" title=\"See cross-reference A\">A</a>)</sup></span></p><p class=\"top-05\"><span class=\"text 3John-1-1\">To my dear friend Gaius, whom I love in the truth.</span></p> <p class=\"top-1\"><span class=\"text 3John-1-2\" id=\"en-NIV-30661\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2\u00a0</sup>Dear friend, I pray that you may enjoy good health and that all may go well with you, even as your soul is getting along well.</span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-3\" id=\"en-NIV-30662\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3\u00a0</sup>It gave me great joy when some believers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30662B\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30662B\" title=\"See cross-reference B\"&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30662B\" title=\"See cross-reference B\">B</a>)</sup> came and testified about your faithfulness to the truth, telling how you continue to walk in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30662C\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30662C\" title=\"See cross-reference C\"&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30662C\" title=\"See cross-reference C\">C</a>)</sup></span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-4\" id=\"en-NIV-30663\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4\u00a0</sup>I have no greater joy than to hear that my children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30663D\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30663D\" title=\"See cross-reference D\"&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30663D\" title=\"See cross-reference D\">D</a>)</sup> are walking in the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30663E\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30663E\" title=\"See cross-reference E\"&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30663E\" title=\"See cross-reference E\">E</a>)</sup></span></p> <p><span class=\"text 3John-1-5\" id=\"en-NIV-30664\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5\u00a0</sup>Dear friend, you are faithful in what you are doing for the brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"footnote\" data-fn=\"#fen-NIV-30664a\" data-link='[&lt;a href=\"#fen-NIV-30664a\" title=\"See footnote a\"&gt;a&lt;/a&gt;]'>[<a href=\"#fen-NIV-30664a\" title=\"See footnote a\">a</a>]</sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30664F\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30664F\" title=\"See cross-reference F\"&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30664F\" title=\"See cross-reference F\">F</a>)</sup> even though they are strangers to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30664G\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30664G\" title=\"See cross-reference G\"&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30664G\" title=\"See cross-reference G\">G</a>)</sup></span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-6\" id=\"en-NIV-30665\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6\u00a0</sup>They have told the church about your love. Please send them on their way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30665H\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30665H\" title=\"See cross-reference H\"&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30665H\" title=\"See cross-reference H\">H</a>)</sup> in a manner that honors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30665I\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30665I\" title=\"See cross-reference I\"&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30665I\" title=\"See cross-reference I\">I</a>)</sup> God.</span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-7\" id=\"en-NIV-30666\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7\u00a0</sup>It was for the sake of the Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30666J\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30666J\" title=\"See cross-reference J\"&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30666J\" title=\"See cross-reference J\">J</a>)</sup> that they went out, receiving no help from the pagans.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30666K\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30666K\" title=\"See cross-reference K\"&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30666K\" title=\"See cross-reference K\">K</a>)</sup></span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-8\" id=\"en-NIV-30667\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8\u00a0</sup>We ought therefore to show hospitality to such people so that we may work together for the truth.</span></p> <p><span class=\"text 3John-1-9\" id=\"en-NIV-30668\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9\u00a0</sup>I wrote to the church, but Diotrephes, who loves to be first, will not welcome us.</span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-10\" id=\"en-NIV-30669\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10\u00a0</sup>So when I come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30669L\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30669L\" title=\"See cross-reference L\"&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30669L\" title=\"See cross-reference L\">L</a>)</sup> I will call attention to what he is doing, spreading malicious nonsense about us. Not satisfied with that, he even refuses to welcome other believers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30669M\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30669M\" title=\"See cross-reference M\"&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30669M\" title=\"See cross-reference M\">M</a>)</sup> He also stops those who want to do so and puts them out of the church.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30669N\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30669N\" title=\"See cross-reference N\"&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30669N\" title=\"See cross-reference N\">N</a>)</sup></span></p> <p><span class=\"text 3John-1-11\" id=\"en-NIV-30670\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11\u00a0</sup>Dear friend, do not imitate what is evil but what is good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30670O\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30670O\" title=\"See cross-reference O\"&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30670O\" title=\"See cross-reference O\">O</a>)</sup> Anyone who does what is good is from God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30670P\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30670P\" title=\"See cross-reference P\"&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30670P\" title=\"See cross-reference P\">P</a>)</sup> Anyone who does what is evil has not seen God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30670Q\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30670Q\" title=\"See cross-reference Q\"&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30670Q\" title=\"See cross-reference Q\">Q</a>)</sup></span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-12\" id=\"en-NIV-30671\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12\u00a0</sup>Demetrius is well spoken of by everyone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30671R\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30671R\" title=\"See cross-reference R\"&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30671R\" title=\"See cross-reference R\">R</a>)</sup>\u2014and even by the truth itself. We also speak well of him, and you know that our testimony is true.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30671S\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30671S\" title=\"See cross-reference S\"&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30671S\" title=\"See cross-reference S\">S</a>)</sup></span></p> <p><span class=\"text 3John-1-13\" id=\"en-NIV-30672\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13\u00a0</sup>I have much to write you, but I do not want to do so with pen and ink.</span> <span class=\"text 3John-1-14\" id=\"en-NIV-30673\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14\u00a0</sup>I hope to see you soon, and we will talk face to face.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30673T\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30673T\" title=\"See cross-reference T\"&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30673T\" title=\"See cross-reference T\">T</a>)</sup></span></p> <p class=\"top-1\"><span class=\"text 3John-1-15\" id=\"en-NIV-30674\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15\u00a0</sup>Peace to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30674U\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30674U\" title=\"See cross-reference U\"&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30674U\" title=\"See cross-reference U\">U</a>)</sup> The friends here send their greetings. Greet the friends there by name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30674V\" data-link='(&lt;a href=\"#cen-NIV-30674V\" title=\"See cross-reference V\"&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)'>(<a href=\"#cen-NIV-30674V\" title=\"See cross-reference V\">V</a>)</sup></span></p> </div>",
        "footnotes_html": "<div class=\"footnotes\">\n<h4>Footnotes</h4><ol><li id=\"fen-NIV-30664a\"><a href=\"#en-NIV-30664\" title=\"Go to 3 John 1:5\">3 John 1:5</a> <span class=\"footnote-text\">The Greek word for <i>brothers and sisters</i> (<i>adelphoi</i>) refers here to believers, both men and women, as part of God\u2019s family.</span></li>\n</ol></div>",
